file.name: schema-alias.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Schemas Component with alias
paths:
  /:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            'application/json':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/UserAlias'
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
    UserAlias:
      $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
